Text: E aí, alguém instalou, funciona e tudo mais?
também gostaria de saber se funciona...

Don't use non-kms activators. Nobody has cracked retail activation. NOBODY.  They have, however, cracked the kms activation *sort-of* using emulated systems in your memory. Thus you have KMSNano, kmsdrunk, kmsmicro, etc.

I recommend getting the most recent version of KMSNano. It includes a Trigger to re-activate whenever you boot-up with less than 30 days left on your activation.
